Help figurines

Figurines of castle guards are mobile way of transporting guards to
wanted location and then morphed into full sized guard.

Different figurines of castle guards can be bought from castle shop at 
(not yet).

Commands:

morph <figurine> - morphs figurine into a guard.
upgrade <figurine> <what> <arg> - upgrades figurine.
	what : level
	arg  : 1-50

See also 'help guards'
